IDENTIFIER: A valid ruby identifier - suitable for class, method and specially variable names
VARIABLE_OR_METHOD_CHAIN:
Any kind of variable name. e.g. @instance, @@class, $global or local.
Possibly following a method call chain
STRING: A simple string literal. e.g. "School's out!"
PARTIAL_HASH_KEY: Part of any hash containing the :partial key
name: Returns the value of attribute name
template: Returns the value of attribute template
